Package gobblin.source.extractor.extract.sftp

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SftpExtractor<S,D>
    Abstract class that implements the SFTP protocol for connecting to source and downloading files
    SftpFsHelper
    Connects to a source via SFTP and executes a given list of SFTP commands
    SftpFsHelper.JSchLogger
    Basic implementation of jsch.Logger that logs the output from the JSch commands to slf4j
    SftpFsHelper.MyUserInfo
    Implementation of UserInfo class for JSch which allows for password-less login via keys
    SftpFsHelper.SftpGetMonitor
    Implementation of an SftpProgressMonitor to monitor the progress of file downloads using the ChannelSftp.GET methods
    SftpLightWeightFileSystem
    A FileSystem implementation that provides the FileSystem interface for an SFTP server.
    SftpSource<S,D>
